'''''Objurium''''' was the [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] that brought [[Kirtan Loor]] to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] from the [[Aggressor (Imperial I-class)|''Aggressor'']] in [[6 ABY/Legends|6.5 ABY]]. It also transported the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] to the Emperor after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], docking at Tower 78, level 443, bay 2 of the [[Imperial Palace/Legends|Imperial Palace]].

